I'm in deep urge of writing here today. I'm in JP's casa. I just finished cooking for them but i'm not hungry because i ate so much doritos for breakfast while reading the script.

NICK is coming out in the March 07 edition of Cosmopolitan! Look for me! i modeled. Check it out. It'll be freakin' awesome.

That's not very important... [looks away and smiles innocently]

I'm taking part in my friend's thesis. He's making a movie. I'm part of it and can't wait to tell my friends about it because they will go on their knees when they find out what my friend is doing!

HAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA

again.
HAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA!!!!!!

I'm sorry. I'm sorry! I'm wiping the happy tears. Hahahahahahahaha.

I had the best fuckin' night of my goddamn fuckin' life! I was mourning like a fuckin girl last night until my friend's from Los Angeles called me at 10pm and told me they heard about my pathetic loss and they wanted to meet up and fuck up my night more. WOULD I SAY NO?!
What I accomplished last night:


  1. First we stopped by my parent's place because my friends wanted to say hello.

  2. Second, we crashed Pierre's hotel and ordered a whole shit load of food and drinks.

  3. We wanted to drink. Marc, Jesse, Sarah, and I went to buy some. When we got back, my friends were playing twister.

  4. Gis brought his Wii. I kicked his ass in poker! There's POKER on Wii! Fuckin WEIRD but Fuckin AWESOME.

  5. Model Dudes and Gals came over to join but there was no more space in the hotel to hold all of us so we moved to Skitz' Apartment and damn man. Everyone went crazy.

  6. We played HS games like suck and pass, spin the bottle, and when we we were all fuckin tipsy, we played who stole the cookie from the cookie jar!


Forget the numbering. It's fuckin up my story! Skitz' got this awesome kid named Rich. He's only 3 years old but he's a bad ass little fucker. He didn't want to go to bed because he wanted to help his dad mix our drinks. He eventually fell asleep on the couch when we were all so tired and wasted.

This group of friends from L.A...I grew up with them. They were all from Canada first but they were all born in L.A. I was the outkast. Hahaha. We used to skate together. the fun days dude. Our parents were good friends so we had no choice but to grow up together.

I didn't have the much sleep because my cousins from mom's side woke me up. They wanted to hang out before they head back to school. Now, I'm up and eating chocolate for breakfast. The other night my cousin came over and we had a wild sleepover. I taught my crazy fuck 15 year old cousin how to roll up a joint. hahaha. We wanted to have solo weird shots all over the house. Fuckers did a good job.

This is for me. Everything's Cool by lit.

this is Nike R. I''m on the phone with Jules and he told me to update for him so, here I am. Doing what he's asking me to do. 

I wish life was easier. I don't blame life though. Life's okay as it is. There are just things that are too much for some to handle. I'm not complaining. I'm just... fucked right now (this is Nike talking). 

"There are reasons why I shouldn't love you and there are reasons why I should stop caring 
But I know this heart of mine was made to fight every painful stare."

I have been working so hard ... My body is kiling me already. I NEED SLEEP. SLEEP. SLEEP. Please send me to bed already. I know my body is getting tired and soon, i'm going to get sick. That's okay. I'm a fuckin' healthy man. lol. What's it going to be? 

I love the nightlife. It's fantastic. Hey Night, Fuck me.

This is why i don't like being in love... one mistake just brings you fuckin down. You expect more than you're supposed you and in the end you get hurt. I'm not running away from pain or the truths about life, it's just, your birthday is the one day you deserve not to have stress. Nice to say that my day wasn't as great until my party. The party is still on going but i'm here because im bummed out and sort of tired. I'm going to start getting wasted at exactly 5am. So, i don't wake up until night. I skip one day.

I think i'm looking for something but i don't know what it is. I think i'm reaching for something that's not grabbing my hand but i don't know what or who will be grabbing it. I've got all these thoughts that I think im bringing out but actually i'm not. I feel like i'm walking on the brick road but really I'm just sinking in quicksand. i'm so tired and abused by myself. I dont know what i want anymore. I feel like i'm slowly being pulled towards my insanity. I feel like i'm failing in something but fuck, i don't know what's making me fail. I think i'm doing things right but everything FEELS wrong. I feel like my only friend are the walls because they give me concrete answers. I feel like my tears have dried up and there's nothing left in me to cry anymore. I feel like my bones are cracking already and i just don't feel it anymore because i'm so distracted by my thoughts. I feel like im insane. I feel like im CRAZY. I hate what i've been given and i'd rather be a kid who has seperated parents. "Every night I hear voices telling me the i should get some sleep because tomorrow might be good...or something. Hold on feeling like i'm heading for a break down and i don't know why..." I'm crazy... I'm going crazy. Please... someone pick me up already... i'm so  tired.... and on the way give me a hug and tell me i'll be alright... I need a life, i need a good one...please...

You know ive heard it said theres beauty in distorion
By some people who withdraw to find their head
And they say theres no humor in misfortune
No, i wonder if they'll laugh when i am dead

Why am i fighting to live
If im just living to fight
Why am i trying to see
When there aint nothing in sight
Why am i trying to give
When no one gives me a try
Why am i dying to live
If im just living to die

You know some people say that values are subjective
But theyre just speaking words
That someone else has said
And so they live and fight and kill with no objective
Sometimes its hard to tell the living from the dead

Why am i fighting to live
If im just living to fight
Why am i trying to see
When there aint nothing in sight
Why am i trying to give
When no one gives me a try
Why am i dying to live
If im just living to die

You know i used to weave
My words into confusion
And so i hope you'll understand me
When im through
You know i used to live my life as an illusion
But reality wil make my dream come true [ :( ]

So ill keep fighting to live
Till theres no reason to fight
And ill keep trying to see
Until the end is in sight
You know im trying to give
So come on
Give me a try
You know im dying to live
Until im ready to die

When i die... this will be my song... if people are planning on singing a song while i'm being buried, please sing this one. This is what i've been fuckin doing my whole life. These are my thoughts and i've been through SHIT that people will never understand. So, i hope you understand these lyrics and undestand me... some know i've been DYING to live... it's just ONE PERSON IN THIS WORLD DOESNT UNDERSTAND WHAT DYING TO LIVE MEANS. I'm still haunted by the thought if im doing the fuckin right thing and i can't live my whole life hiding and trying to push my thoughts away. I WANT TO JUST UNDERSTAND WHY IM HERE AND WHY AM I NOT THINKING STRAIGHT. I know people tell me i'm different and i'm special because i've done miracle in sickness and i never tried to blame myself or others for my misfortunes... thank you... thank you for seeing that but there are things that you don't see because i don't show it....

Welcome to the real world, she said to me
Condescendingly
Take a seat
Take your life
Plot it out in black and white
Well I never lived the dreams of the prom kings
And the drama queens
I'd like to think the best of me
Is still hidin'
Up my sleeve

They love to tell you
Stay inside the lines
But something's better
On the other side

I wanna run through the halls of my high school
I wanna scream at the top of my lungs
I just found out there's no such thing as the real world
Just a lie you've got to rise above

So the good boys and girls take the so called right track
Faded white hat
Grabbing credits
And maybe transfers
They read all the books but they can't find the answers
And all of our parents
They're getting older
I wonder if they've wished for anything better
While in their memories
Tiny tragedies

They love to tell you
Stay inside the lines
But something's better
On the other side

I wanna run through the halls of my high school
I wanna scream at the top of my lungs
I just found out there's no such thing as the real world
Just a lie you got to rise above

I am invincible, I am invincible, I am invincible
As long as I'm alive

I wanna run through the halls of my high school
I wanna scream at the top of my lungs
I just found out there's no such thing as the real world
Just a lie you've got to rise above

I just can't wait til my 10th year reunion
I'm gonna bust down the double doors
And when I stand on these tables before you
You will know what all this time was for

My life's just fucked.
I know you're what i want but it's all wrong and that hurts me.

on the other hand... I wanna sing a love song and know the thoughts inside her head... I wanna know i'm the one she wants. I'm so scared to tell her that i love her so much because she might not understand what that means. I'm scared that she'll back off if i tell her my thoughts...

on the other hand... I don't know why but your love can make these things better because i know you've done it before despite the pain...

on the other hand... everything is new with you... my life's in a rush here but i know yours isn't... i don't want to scare you...


MOM.... I LOVE YOU.... I NEED YOU RIGHT NOW BUT THAT'S FUCKIN IMPOSSIBLE.
DAD... how are you up there... is your life better? I pray that one day ill be able to join you and you can tell me your stories and tell me i'm a shit for not understanding a lot of things.
brother... how are you... please don't break... i need you too. i dont want to lose you too...

I was thinking about something and realized that Life isn't that bad.
Everyone says life sucks but what do they think? Life is supposed to be the Garden of Eden? What kind of world would we have if it was perfect. No war, no pollution, no crime, all peace, no love. Don't they ever think that all these "sucky" shit that happens to us are all wake up calls (maybe)? Or they have purposes? A lot of people blame God but don't they think that maybe God is doing all this to open our eyes or punish us? We were the ones that do all the bad things not GOD. So why blame him? It's irrational you know. Man is all about "me,me,me" and men think they're not like that but they are! If people really cared then they would care to stand up and make a change. We all here that "somethin small could make a big difference in the world" but how many actually follow that? If we picture the world.... one person could pick up a can of soda that's on the street and throw it (that makes a difference) but if you zoom out to ALL THE STREETS IN THE WORLD, people jus pass by. What difference did the person who threw the can make? Nothing. In the world we live in now, it's not "the small things could make a difference anymore." My point is... Life doesnt suck because sll these negative experiences are just lessons. It makes us open our eyes. Man is too sel-centered to actually see that.
Even im like that. self-centered, doesnt think. blah blah.
